# close是收盘值，即当天的数据
close =  np.array([float(x) for x in bitCoin_data['Value']])
# 技术指标
bitCoin_data['SMA10'] = talib.SMA(close, timeperiod=10)
bitCoin_data['SMA20'] = talib.SMA(close, timeperiod=20)
bitCoin_data['SMA30'] = talib.SMA(close, timeperiod=30)

bitCoin_data['SMA10'].fillna(method='bfill', inplace=True)
bitCoin_data['SMA20'].fillna(method='bfill', inplace=True)
bitCoin_data['SMA30'].fillna(method='bfill', inplace=True)

# 可视化
fig = plt.figure(figsize=[12, 8])
ax = fig.add_subplot(111)
ax.plot(np.arange(0, len(bitCoin_data)), bitCoin_data['SMA10'])
ax.plot(np.arange(0, len(bitCoin_data)), bitCoin_data['SMA20'])
ax.plot(np.arange(0, len(bitCoin_data)), bitCoin_data['SMA30'])

# 设置坐标轴格式
def format_date(x, pos=None):
    if x < 0 or x > len(bitCoin_data['Date']) - 1:
        return ''
    return bitCoin_data['Date'][int(x)]
ax.xaxis.set_major_formatter(ticker.FuncFormatter(format_date))
plt.setp(plt.gca().get_xticklabels(), rotation=45, horizontalalignment='right')
plt.show()

MACD指标可视化（不提取特征）¶

In [ ]:
fig = plt.figure(figsize=(12, 8))
ax = fig.add_subplot(111)

dif, dea, bar = talib.MACD(close, fastperiod=12, slowperiod=26, signalperiod=9)
dif[np.isnan(dif)], dea[np.isnan(dea)], bar[np.isnan(bar)] = 0, 0, 0

tmp_len = 300 # 控制绘制的天数
ax.plot(np.arange(0, tmp_len), dif[:tmp_len])
ax.plot(np.arange(0, tmp_len), dea[:tmp_len])
red_bar = np.where(bar > 0, 2 * bar, 0)
blue_bar = np.where(bar < 0, 2 * bar, 0)
ax.bar(np.arange(0, tmp_len), red_bar[:tmp_len], color="red")
ax.bar(np.arange(0, tmp_len), blue_bar[:tmp_len], color="blue")

ax.xaxis.set_major_locator(ticker.MaxNLocator(20))
ax.xaxis.set_major_formatter(ticker.FuncFormatter(format_date))
plt.setp(plt.gca().get_xticklabels(), rotation=45, horizontalalignment='right')
plt.show()

完整的特征提取¶

In [ ]:
# 特征提取函数
def feature_selection(df):
    # MA
    df['SMA10'] = talib.SMA(close, timeperiod=10)
    df['SMA20'] = talib.SMA(close, timeperiod=20)
    df['SMA30'] = talib.SMA(close, timeperiod=30)
    # MACD特征
    df['MACD'], df['MACDsignal'], df['MACDhist'] = talib.MACD(
        close, fastperiod=12, slowperiod=26, signalperiod=9)
    # 其他特征
    df['EMA12'] = talib.EMA(close, timeperiod=6)
    df['EMA26'] = talib.EMA(close, timeperiod=12)
    df['RSI'] = talib.RSI(close, timeperiod=12)
    # 动量指标
    df['MOM'] = talib.MOM(close, timeperiod=5)
    df['ROC'] = talib.ROC(close, timeperiod=10)
    df['ROCP'] = talib.ROCP(close, timeperiod=10)
    df['ROCR'] = talib.ROCR(close, timeperiod=10)
    df['ROCR100'] = talib.ROCR100(close, timeperiod=10)
    # 新添加特征
    df['MOM'] = talib.MOM(close)
    df['HT_DCPERIOD'] = talib.HT_DCPERIOD(close)
    df['HT_DCPHASE'] = talib.HT_DCPHASE(close)
    df['SINE'],  df['LEADSINE'] = talib.HT_SINE(close)
    df['INPHASE'],  df['QUADRATURE'] = talib.HT_PHASOR(close)
    df['APO'] = talib.APO(close)
    df['PPO'] = talib.PPO(close)
    # df['MACD'],  df['MACD_SIG'],  df['MACD_HIST'] = talib.MACD(close)
    df['CMO'] = talib.CMO(close)
    df['ROCP'] = talib.ROCP(close)
    df['TRIX'] = talib.TRIX(close)
    df['RSI'] = talib.RSI(close)
    #填充空缺值
    df.fillna(method='bfill', inplace=True)
    return df

def format_date(x, pos=None):
    # 由于前面股票数据在 date 这个位置传入的都是int
    # 因此 x=0,1,2,...
    # date_tickers 是所有日期的字符串形式列表
    if x < 0 or x > len(bitCoin_data['Date']) - 1:
        return ''
    return bitCoin_data['Date'][int(x)]
